WEBVTT

00:00.174 --> 00:05.122
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:06.094 --> 00:08.802
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.934 --> 00:13.942
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.966 --> 00:18.722
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.758 --> 00:22.786
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.790 --> 00:27.734
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.758 --> 00:31.030
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:31.054 --> 00:34.518
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.542 --> 00:39.790
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.790 --> 00:41.408
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.408 --> 00:44.886
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.910 --> 00:48.182
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.206 --> 00:53.878
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.902 --> 00:55.246
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.246 --> 00:58.582
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.606 --> 01:01.954
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:02.062 --> 01:07.259
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.259 --> 01:08.942
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.942 --> 01:12.342
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.366 --> 01:15.766
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.790 --> 01:21.366
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.390 --> 01:24.802
♪ I love you ♪

01:27.080 --> 01:27.870
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.870 --> 01:30.943
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 31=

01:30.943 --> 01:35.510
(I want to marry you, Sheng.)

02:01.236 --> 02:04.215
- I'm hungry.
- You are?

02:14.836 --> 02:20.495
- What do you want to eat?
- Coconut rice.

02:22.676 --> 02:24.055
Since I met you,

02:28.875 --> 02:31.215
I've used up all the vacation days
I've saved for years.

02:34.155 --> 02:40.255
Does that mean
our next trip will be years away?

02:42.995 --> 02:44.055
It's possible.

02:52.035 --> 02:57.336
However, sometimes I have meetings
all over the country.

02:58.715 --> 03:00.176
If you have the time,

03:01.475 --> 03:06.215
during breaks from meetings,
I can accompany you to snack streets,

03:07.315 --> 03:09.095
famous sites, and such.

03:18.995 --> 03:23.255
I've gotten used
to seeing you every day,

03:24.356 --> 03:29.215
seeing you all day long,
and saying goodnight face-to-face.

04:34.795 --> 04:37.651
- What are you doing?
- It's too hot. I'm going back.

04:37.675 --> 04:43.175
- Too... Take me with you.
- You're such a tag-along.

04:44.115 --> 04:47.732
The parting is near, and the atmosphere
between them is killing me.

04:47.756 --> 04:49.535
I can't stay here anymore.

05:07.556 --> 05:09.336
The weather today is good, isn't it?

05:11.076 --> 05:12.896
The breeze is quite comfortable too.

05:52.396 --> 05:53.456
You are awake.

05:56.396 --> 05:57.615
Did you sleep well?

06:02.196 --> 06:04.016
There are less than 20 hours left.

06:04.795 --> 06:09.735
Let's find something to do.
Don't waste this rare holiday.

06:29.956 --> 06:34.936
- What are you doing here? Isn't it hot?
- She...

06:37.836 --> 06:41.891
The sunshine is nice. It'd be a waste
if we didn't come out to bask.

06:41.915 --> 06:46.975
Also, there are fruits and water here.
It's nice that we play with our phones.

06:50.475 --> 06:53.812
(Actually, she has to go back,
but she doesn't want to part with you.)

06:53.836 --> 06:58.975
(She doesn't want to disturb you.
So she sits here to see more of you.)

07:00.556 --> 07:03.336
We are going out to eat in a while.
Why not join us?

07:04.316 --> 07:08.891
- Are you sure? Aren't you on a date?
- It's okay. Let's go together.

07:08.915 --> 07:12.175
What's with the reservedness?
Let's go. It's such a good opportunity.

07:12.595 --> 07:15.696
Yeah, the more, the merrier.
Let's go together.

07:18.595 --> 07:21.571
If you don't mind,
I'll go back to the room to get my bag.

07:21.595 --> 07:23.535
- I'll go get a power bank.
- Okay.

07:27.795 --> 07:30.091
She's your fan.
She wants to see more of you.

07:30.115 --> 07:33.456
- She's afraid she won't see you again.
- I guessed it.

07:33.956 --> 07:35.456
You could even guess this?

07:36.196 --> 07:39.571
There must be a reason why you
suddenly invited them to eat with us.

07:39.595 --> 07:41.175
It was easy to figure it out.

07:53.756 --> 07:54.816
What's wrong?

08:01.436 --> 08:05.735
Mr. Mo, how about we see
who can get to the platform first?

08:06.396 --> 08:07.496
Sure.

08:16.915 --> 08:19.771
- Dong Yiru, what are you doing?
- I just don't want you to win.

08:19.795 --> 08:23.371
I'll tell my aunt
to dock your pay when I get back.

08:23.395 --> 08:26.416
- Then I'll accuse you of jobbery.
- They are quite interesting.

08:26.475 --> 08:30.015
They're often like this.
I'm used to it. My brother is too.

08:31.276 --> 08:33.686
Why don't we take a break over there
and enjoy the view there?

08:33.686 --> 08:34.686
Okay.

08:35.995 --> 08:37.336
Ouch!

08:37.956 --> 08:39.975
- I'm going up.
- Let's go.

08:40.235 --> 08:42.576
You can't catch up.

08:48.676 --> 08:52.495
It's so beautiful. So pretty.

08:52.755 --> 08:56.691
The weather is so good. It'd be nice
if it could be like this every day.

08:56.715 --> 08:58.331
Yeah, it'd be nice
if every day could be like this.

08:58.355 --> 09:00.851
If you do this every day,
it will be the end of me.

09:00.875 --> 09:05.416
I'm in a good mood today.
I'll let you off.

09:11.036 --> 09:14.975
Yiru, these are for you.

09:16.055 --> 09:17.508
(Qiang Qingci)

09:17.635 --> 09:19.095
For me?

09:23.408 --> 09:26.020
(Autographs
of all the Perfect Voice members)

09:26.276 --> 09:28.495
The autographs of all of you!

09:28.796 --> 09:31.375
Thank you very much for supporting us.

09:32.755 --> 09:35.855
- Well...
- Say thank you.

09:37.196 --> 09:41.371
Thank you, Mr. Mo. I couldn't get these
even after waiting in line last time.

09:41.395 --> 09:43.276
Could you express my gratitude

09:43.276 --> 09:45.635
to the other members who are not here?
I've liked you guys for a long time.

09:45.635 --> 09:47.971
Alright, no need to be polite with me.
We are friends now.

09:47.995 --> 09:50.215
We will see each other again
in the future, right?

09:51.715 --> 09:52.975
Wait.

09:53.715 --> 09:57.495
Alright, if you want to thank them,
you can tell them yourself.

09:57.556 --> 09:58.776
Okay.

09:59.436 --> 10:02.735
- Alright.
- Sheng, you are amazing.

10:02.836 --> 10:04.892
- Let me take a look.
- No.

10:04.916 --> 10:07.615
Stingy. So few?

10:10.836 --> 10:12.416
Like I said,

10:12.916 --> 10:14.975
there is definitely no problem
with Mr. Mo's character.

10:15.676 --> 10:17.436
- He's really not bad.
- Right?

10:17.436 --> 10:21.772
But it's still early days.
There is a long way to go.

10:21.796 --> 10:24.456
Being confident in him today
doesn't mean forever.

10:25.316 --> 10:28.571
Mr. Mo is genuine gold.
He can definitely withstand any test.

10:28.595 --> 10:30.135
It's starting again, huh?

10:31.715 --> 10:33.691
- Oh, my goodness.
- Let me see.

10:33.715 --> 10:34.956
- No.
- Just one.

10:34.956 --> 10:36.816
- No.
- This one.

10:38.715 --> 10:39.776
Don't!

10:40.836 --> 10:43.211
- What's the matter?
- You are so annoying.

10:43.235 --> 10:47.215
So precious?
Okay, I'll take them all then.

10:49.316 --> 10:50.456
Thank you.

10:55.916 --> 10:57.135
Thank you all as well.

11:30.635 --> 11:32.375
I'll go get the luggage first.

11:58.316 --> 12:00.536
Then, I'm leaving.

12:03.355 --> 12:06.336
Call me when you get home.

12:06.875 --> 12:08.056
Okay.

12:21.196 --> 12:23.215
I don't want to let you go
all of a sudden.

12:25.395 --> 12:28.456
I just toughened up to say goodbye,
but now I've lost that feeling.

12:31.956 --> 12:36.336
Then, how about I accompany you upstairs
to meet your parents?

12:38.676 --> 12:40.296
They are all asleep.

12:42.076 --> 12:43.735
I was joking with you.

12:44.235 --> 12:45.776
You scared me.

13:00.836 --> 13:03.936
Well, I'm really leaving now.

13:08.755 --> 13:12.336
- Good night.
- Good night.

13:20.635 --> 13:22.975
- Bye.
- Bye.

13:37.916 --> 13:39.052
- Let's go.
- Okay.

13:39.076 --> 13:40.076
Go.

13:43.995 --> 13:45.576
Don't be reluctant.

14:52.156 --> 14:53.215
Still not sleeping?

14:54.995 --> 14:56.255
I slept enough.

15:03.515 --> 15:05.135
Did you?

15:05.875 --> 15:07.135
Or are you bothered?

15:14.115 --> 15:18.696
The whole world knows you like her,
but you refuse to admit it.

15:26.515 --> 15:28.375
I just fear that once it starts,

15:28.875 --> 15:32.015
we won't even be able to be friends
if we break up.

15:45.916 --> 15:49.095
You forced out my inner thoughts.
Aren't you going to comment?

15:50.436 --> 15:51.615
I have no opinion.

15:52.156 --> 15:53.296
I wish you good luck.

15:54.676 --> 15:56.416
I didn't say I was going to confess.

15:57.235 --> 15:58.456
It's a wish in advance.

16:00.316 --> 16:02.975
What if I get rejected after confessing?

16:10.595 --> 16:11.975
Show your sincerity

16:12.595 --> 16:13.696
and keep up.

16:30.778 --> 16:32.644
(Mo Qingcheng)

16:45.196 --> 16:46.215
Hello?

16:46.276 --> 16:49.095
I couldn't sleep well,
so I came straight to the hospital.

16:49.576 --> 16:51.015
Did you sleep well last night?

16:52.676 --> 16:53.976
I miss you.

16:57.115 --> 16:58.216
For how much?

17:03.996 --> 17:07.135
I miss you a lot.

17:11.955 --> 17:15.371
I'll go to the supermarket later
and see if they have coconuts.

17:15.395 --> 17:17.175
Don't you want to eat coconut rice?

17:20.635 --> 17:21.736
I'll make it for you.

17:25.316 --> 17:27.976
Still sleepy? Go back to sleep.

17:32.395 --> 17:35.776
- Go.
- Okay. Bye.

17:58.435 --> 18:00.816
- Mao.
- We are back!

18:01.155 --> 18:03.651
- You are back.
- We brought you some local specialties.

18:03.675 --> 18:07.336
- Right.
- I'm glad you guys remembered me.

18:07.476 --> 18:10.695
It wasn't in vain that I worked overtime
every night to let you two run wild.

18:10.915 --> 18:13.855
Isn't it because your wife
wouldn't let you go with us?

18:13.915 --> 18:16.611
Nonsense. That's called respect.

18:16.635 --> 18:18.875
How could Mao leave his wife
alone at home during the holiday?

18:18.875 --> 18:22.375
Alright. How was this trip?

18:24.195 --> 18:27.536
I heard that Shengshengman's brother
went too.

18:27.796 --> 18:31.131
Don't mention it.
Her brother was like a hovering hawk,

18:31.155 --> 18:32.732
following her closely.

18:32.756 --> 18:36.976
If it were not for us holding him back,
Mo's vacation would have been in vain.

18:37.796 --> 18:39.935
Will her brother
talk nonsense when he goes back?

18:40.276 --> 18:44.496
Shouldn't you have a little more faith
in our prominent figure?

18:44.595 --> 18:48.056
Or we would've soaked her brother
in water for three hours for nothing.

18:48.195 --> 18:49.796
- Right.
- His skin was all wrinkled.

18:49.796 --> 18:53.331
- Soaked in water?
- It was a pool party.

18:53.355 --> 18:56.296
- It was fun.
- Good for you.

18:56.516 --> 18:59.131
Mao, do you know? During this vacation,

18:59.155 --> 19:02.895
the relationship between Mo and Sheng
has been gradually warming up.

19:03.076 --> 19:05.812
But the luckiest one
is actually someone else.

19:05.836 --> 19:08.655
By all accounts,
Zhou Zheng should also pick up the pace.

19:08.955 --> 19:12.891
He seems like a lady-killer.
But when it comes to a critical moment,

19:12.915 --> 19:15.171
his cowardice makes me anxious.

19:15.195 --> 19:17.212
- How did you know?
- Right, how did you know?

19:17.236 --> 19:18.816
How couldn't I know?

19:19.675 --> 19:23.091
You sit at home and know everything
that's happening in the world.

19:23.115 --> 19:25.455
- You are admirable.
- It's nothing.

19:26.875 --> 19:28.171
- For me?
- Yes.

19:28.195 --> 19:32.576
- Thank you, then.
- Mao, I bought it.

19:34.076 --> 19:36.131
- Let's get to work.
- Okay.

19:36.155 --> 19:39.331
- Just warm it up, and you can eat.
- He knows. No need to remind him.

19:39.355 --> 19:41.655
- Let's start working.
- I chose it.

19:49.635 --> 19:51.115
- Haven't I told you?
- Stop.

19:51.115 --> 19:54.371
Just watch TV at home and rest well
during the weekends.

19:54.395 --> 19:57.316
Didn't we come here just to help you
with the housework? Third brother.

19:57.316 --> 19:58.816
- Brother...
- Third brother.

19:59.595 --> 20:01.131
- Yes?
- I told you to collect the laundry.

20:01.155 --> 20:05.595
- How could you let Sheng do that?
- I forgot. I am cooking fish.

20:05.595 --> 20:09.016
If you were busy, let me know.
Hurry up to check on that fish.

20:09.115 --> 20:10.556
- Alright.
- It's okay.

20:10.556 --> 20:12.175
Come on. Have a seat.

20:13.036 --> 20:14.736
I'll help you with that.

20:16.236 --> 20:20.395
S-Sheng, a-a buddy of mine
sent me a message saying

20:20.395 --> 20:23.076
the hospital across from our store is on fire
and the firefighters have gone there.

20:23.076 --> 20:26.155
- It's on fire? What happened?
- I'll make a call. Gu Jia is there.

20:26.155 --> 20:27.695
Right. Ask him now.

20:31.716 --> 20:35.455
- How is it?
- He's not answering. I'll try again.

20:45.516 --> 20:47.976
I will go take a look myself.
He's not answering the phone.

20:50.884 --> 20:51.395
(Mo Qingcheng)

20:51.395 --> 20:52.716
- Sheng, are you going out?
- Sorry,

20:52.716 --> 20:54.935
the number you have dialed
is powered off.

20:58.155 --> 21:01.056
Sorry, the number you have dialed...

21:17.435 --> 21:21.651
- Hello, Sheng, what's up?
- Xiaoxing, can you get in touch with Juemei?

21:21.675 --> 21:23.415
G-Get in touch with him?

21:24.955 --> 21:27.976
I-I might not be able to do that.

21:28.516 --> 21:32.252
- Is there something wrong?
- Mo's cell phone is switched off.

21:32.276 --> 21:34.212
I don't know what happened,
and I can't find him.

21:34.236 --> 21:36.692
Now, I don't know whether I should
go to the hospital or his place.

21:36.716 --> 21:38.776
I want to ask Juemei
if he's home or not.

21:39.955 --> 21:45.816
Perhaps his phone will be turned on
in a while. Don't worry.

21:48.355 --> 21:52.131
What's wrong? Your voice sounds like
something has happened.

21:52.155 --> 21:56.175
His hospital is on fire. I can't find him.
I'm really worried about him.

21:56.716 --> 22:01.415
I'm sure he's okay. Perhaps his phone
is just out of battery, right?

22:01.516 --> 22:03.256
How can you be sure?

22:08.996 --> 22:13.536
It's just... I believe in my heart
that he's okay.

22:16.355 --> 22:18.816
Have you seen where Mo is?

22:21.556 --> 22:22.816
Geng Xiaoxing!

22:26.716 --> 22:32.736
I'll tell you the truth.
I'm at Juemei's place.

22:34.915 --> 22:38.816
Come over. It seems Mr. Mo is sleeping.

22:40.556 --> 22:44.536
- Alright, I'm coming now. Bye.
- I actually haven't...

23:47.595 --> 23:49.375
Juemei woke me up.

23:49.875 --> 23:52.816
He said you were coming over. What's up?

23:58.236 --> 23:59.415
Did you miss me?

24:22.476 --> 24:24.496
Is your phone out of battery?

24:25.076 --> 24:26.216
Out of battery?

24:31.635 --> 24:33.216
Seems like it is out of battery.

25:00.395 --> 25:03.855
I really wish to see you every day
when I wake up.

25:09.516 --> 25:11.496
I worked overtime
until 2 a.m. last night.

25:13.236 --> 25:14.655
You just woke up?

25:17.915 --> 25:22.056
I slept for less than two hours.

25:25.115 --> 25:26.976
I'm still sleepy.

25:33.115 --> 25:35.175
Can you sleep with me for a while?

25:49.155 --> 25:51.296
There are fresh coconuts in the fridge.

25:52.756 --> 25:54.976
I'll make you
some coconut rice in a bit.

25:57.435 --> 25:59.175
You bought them?

26:00.115 --> 26:02.935
Is that enough for four people?

26:05.915 --> 26:07.216
It's not for four people.

26:08.915 --> 26:10.336
Just you and me.

26:13.756 --> 26:17.615
Are Juemei and Xiaoxing
going out to eat?

26:21.435 --> 26:22.455
Sheng,

26:25.955 --> 26:31.336
do you want to see me every day?

26:33.036 --> 26:34.336
Yes, I do.

26:35.276 --> 26:38.615
But you are very busy.

26:39.675 --> 26:41.095
I can understand that.

26:42.675 --> 26:46.296
My grandfather was also this busy
when he was young.

26:46.955 --> 26:48.615
He often tells me about that.

26:50.955 --> 26:52.655
Do you

26:55.195 --> 26:57.175
want to be able to find me at any time?

26:59.115 --> 27:00.496
Of course, I do.

27:02.316 --> 27:03.935
Do you want

27:06.195 --> 27:08.536
to sleep in our bed, waiting for me

27:09.476 --> 27:11.816
to come back at dawn,
even when I'm not home at night

27:12.556 --> 27:14.296
because of work?

27:26.476 --> 27:27.976
Do you

27:31.955 --> 27:34.016
want to hear my voice every day

27:37.236 --> 27:38.496
and have me

27:41.076 --> 27:43.016
lull you to sleep,
no matter how late it is?

27:51.915 --> 27:52.935
Yes, I do.

27:57.155 --> 27:58.256
I'm glad that you do.

28:03.756 --> 28:05.095
So,

28:08.036 --> 28:09.455
from now on,

28:11.516 --> 28:12.976
it's just you and me.

28:16.796 --> 28:19.135
I'll only cook for my wife.

28:38.955 --> 28:40.135
Are you shocked?

28:45.155 --> 28:46.655
We are on the bed now.

28:47.716 --> 28:51.415
How could you

28:52.796 --> 28:55.935
ask...

28:57.435 --> 28:58.576
Ask for what?

29:01.955 --> 29:03.855
Ask...

29:12.036 --> 29:13.336
Ask...

29:22.756 --> 29:25.095
- Ask...
- I ask you to marry me.

29:42.155 --> 29:44.996
I want to marry you, Sheng.

29:44.996 --> 29:47.760
♪ My heart is racing ♪

29:48.679 --> 29:52.729
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

29:52.729 --> 29:57.686
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

29:58.672 --> 30:01.782
♪ What kind of look ♪

30:02.503 --> 30:06.436
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

30:06.915 --> 30:09.655
I'm still so sleepy.

30:10.556 --> 30:12.496
Then sleep a little longer.

30:14.316 --> 30:18.095
I just proposed. I'm in a good mood.

30:18.635 --> 30:19.935
I can't sleep anymore.

30:20.203 --> 30:23.285
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

30:23.285 --> 30:26.945
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

30:26.945 --> 30:31.780
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

30:31.875 --> 30:33.536
Feels like something's missing.

30:47.456 --> 30:52.771
♪ Hey, I have decided ♪

30:53.510 --> 30:56.403
♪ In every starry sky ♪

30:57.598 --> 31:01.232
♪ I want to get closer to you ♪

31:01.232 --> 31:06.734
♪ Hey, I want to hug you ♪

31:06.919 --> 31:09.878
♪ I've never been so sure ♪

31:11.098 --> 31:15.841
♪ I miss you so much ♪

31:18.155 --> 31:19.695
What are you looking for?

31:26.355 --> 31:28.935
Why is it so quiet? What are they doing?

31:30.076 --> 31:33.611
Why do you care? They are adults.
It's none of your business.

31:33.635 --> 31:35.875
- Lower your voice.
- It's not necessary.

31:35.875 --> 31:38.331
Why did you pull me in just now?

31:38.355 --> 31:43.611
How are we going to explain it
when Sheng comes out later?

31:43.635 --> 31:45.816
Explain what?
There's nothing to explain.

31:47.435 --> 31:49.175
What? Isn't there?

31:52.595 --> 31:58.452
Well. If you say there's something,
that's it, okay?

31:58.476 --> 32:00.135
If you say there isn't,

32:01.476 --> 32:04.935
- there's nothing.
- Why are you laughing? What "nothing"?

32:05.675 --> 32:07.655
Isn't it just that... you know?

32:08.195 --> 32:10.655
Okay, don't stand here. Have a seat.

32:10.716 --> 32:14.135
What should we say later,
if Sheng finds out?

32:20.276 --> 32:22.016
Let me tell you a story.

32:24.635 --> 32:25.635
Okay.

32:28.996 --> 32:35.615
(A few years ago, one day
I was resting in the on-call room.)

32:47.435 --> 32:50.175
How many night shifts did you have
to make you so tired?

32:50.616 --> 32:51.935
I don't remember clearly.

32:52.875 --> 32:56.216
- Eat something.
- Thank you.

33:07.796 --> 33:08.816
It's delicious.

33:10.355 --> 33:13.571
Our club wants
to make an album this year.

33:13.595 --> 33:15.976
They asked me
to help select a dozen songs.

33:16.516 --> 33:18.816
- Could you listen to them for me?
- Okay.

33:23.756 --> 33:24.816
Here we go.

33:25.335 --> 33:28.196
(Murky Wine Spilling Down)

33:32.435 --> 33:33.655
Next one?

33:35.376 --> 33:38.500
(Viewing the World Drunkenly)

33:48.946 --> 33:50.160
(Untitled)

33:50.160 --> 33:55.023
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

33:57.551 --> 34:02.589
♪ The morning breeze
was blowing in the lotus pond ♪

34:04.775 --> 34:10.964
♪ The ruqun dress and the paper umbrella ♪

34:12.007 --> 34:17.800
♪ Couldn't hide my ignorance ♪

34:19.335 --> 34:24.513
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

34:25.735 --> 34:29.892
♪ The sunset stained my face slightly red ♪

34:29.892 --> 34:31.686
(Untitled)

34:32.875 --> 34:34.575
Why doesn't this song have a name?

34:35.316 --> 34:37.296
You also think it sounds good, right?

34:39.435 --> 34:43.776
The arrangement, composition,
and the vocal are all quite good.

34:45.236 --> 34:48.256
Who is the composer?
And who's the singer?

34:49.515 --> 34:51.296
Too bad I can't find the composer.

34:55.276 --> 34:56.336
You can't?

34:57.196 --> 35:01.011
We heard this song
in the library of submitted songs.

35:01.035 --> 35:04.612
Many new composers
submit their music to us.

35:04.636 --> 35:08.415
We all thought this song
was particularly good after finding it.

35:08.475 --> 35:11.411
But it has no name
and no information about the composer.

35:11.435 --> 35:14.491
As you know,
I take copyright issues very seriously.

35:14.515 --> 35:17.535
If I can't find the composer,
I can't use it.

35:20.676 --> 35:24.816
How about you send this song to me,
and I'll try to find its composer?

35:40.756 --> 35:43.616
(Then I searched
a lot of music libraries.)

35:44.236 --> 35:49.055
(Back then, a lot of the music libraries
had incomplete song information.)

35:50.435 --> 35:54.776
(I couldn't find that voice.)

36:03.355 --> 36:06.535
You're not going to tell me
it's the song I uploaded?

36:07.676 --> 36:08.776
What do you think?

36:09.395 --> 36:14.051
I did record and upload a few demos.
I was a complete newbie at that time.

36:14.075 --> 36:17.256
I didn't even get an online ID.
I was just singing for fun.

36:18.035 --> 36:21.371
And I don't even remember
how many platforms I uploaded it to.

36:21.395 --> 36:25.851
There were hundreds of similar pieces
to download back then, all nameless.

36:25.875 --> 36:27.656
How did you know it was me?

36:28.676 --> 36:31.816
- I didn't.
- Then...

36:32.836 --> 36:37.216
I searched for a long time
and got no results, so I gave up.

36:39.355 --> 36:41.015
But I remember your voice.

36:41.915 --> 36:42.975
It's very special.

36:44.496 --> 36:46.535
Even if years had passed
before I heard it again,

36:47.975 --> 36:49.336
I could still recognize it.

36:55.236 --> 37:01.055
(Feng Yasong and I would go to various
unfamiliar chat rooms to listen to people talk.)

37:02.116 --> 37:03.824
(Both of us are busy with work.)

37:03.824 --> 37:06.756
(Shengshengman)
(But a dubbing actor needs to experience life.)

37:06.756 --> 37:09.115
- (Listening to strangers' chat)
- That pepper pork belly chicken is superb.

37:09.115 --> 37:10.495
(is kind of a method.)

37:11.995 --> 37:16.531
We ordered a red and white pot.
The white part is fresh soup.

37:16.555 --> 37:19.296
The red part is blood and tofu
from Taiwan, China.

37:20.116 --> 37:23.760
(Shengshengman)
Do you know how great that soup

37:23.760 --> 37:26.252
- tastes?
- Sheng,

37:26.276 --> 37:29.455
are you tormenting yourself
or taking revenge on me?

37:30.276 --> 37:33.051
(Shengshengman)
To be honest, it's my first time knowing

37:33.075 --> 37:36.495
pork belly and chicken stewed together
are so tasty.

37:36.596 --> 37:39.931
Imagine brewing the soup
until it turns milky white.

37:39.955 --> 37:43.455
And it is filled with a rich taste
of herbs and the aroma of pepper.

37:44.756 --> 37:46.812
I swear, that one next to the hospital

37:46.836 --> 37:49.575
absolutely ranks in the top three
of pork belly chicken hotpots.

37:57.316 --> 37:58.935
Why aren't you speaking?

38:05.955 --> 38:08.055
This is a famous Hakka dish
from Guangdong.

38:09.196 --> 38:10.776
If you have time,

38:11.676 --> 38:12.856
you can also make it at home.

38:12.880 --> 38:14.716
(Qiang Qingci)

38:14.716 --> 38:18.616
Actually, it's not hard to make it.
It just needs some time.

38:18.836 --> 38:22.216
And cleaning the pork belly
can be a bit troublesome.

38:22.515 --> 38:25.656
Try to have all the ingredients.
It will be very nourishing.

38:25.915 --> 38:33.575
I remember there are red dates,
codonopsis, polygonatum, and goji berries.

38:34.475 --> 38:37.696
The rest
are some commonly used seasonings,

38:38.116 --> 38:39.895
such as salt and white peppercorns.

38:40.636 --> 38:41.696
Of course,

38:42.636 --> 38:46.851
- you also need cooking wine and ginger.
- Can you hear me talking?

38:46.875 --> 38:50.015
Put the chicken inside the pork belly
and seal the pork belly with toothpicks.

38:50.636 --> 38:51.975
Then simmer them.

38:53.875 --> 38:56.656
I'm in a tunnel.
The signal is not very good.

38:58.716 --> 39:02.776
(Then one day. I was working overtime
and went to a supermarket to buy things.)

39:06.760 --> 39:08.770
(Wangjia Supermarket)

39:08.770 --> 39:12.180
♪ The morning breeze was blowing
in the lotus pond ♪

39:14.152 --> 39:20.548
♪ The ruqun dress and the paper umbrella ♪

39:21.384 --> 39:27.073
♪ Couldn't hide my ignorance ♪

39:28.744 --> 39:33.784
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

39:36.072 --> 39:40.676
♪ The dragonflies stood on the water
in the afternoon ♪

39:40.716 --> 39:41.895
Then what?

39:42.636 --> 39:43.696
Then?

39:46.995 --> 39:48.736
Then...

39:49.636 --> 39:53.696
- It's time to make coconut rice.
- Why don't you finish the story?

39:53.836 --> 39:55.935
Finish it first.

40:09.836 --> 40:11.776
- Mr. Mo.
- You are here.

40:11.836 --> 40:12.895
Sheng.

40:20.636 --> 40:24.092
Zheng, didn't you say you were alone?

40:24.116 --> 40:27.732
This makes me feel very embarrassed.
I should have invited Feishao over too.

40:27.756 --> 40:30.616
- What's to be embarrassed about? Sit.
- Fine.

40:34.515 --> 40:35.535
Continue.

40:36.196 --> 40:38.172
- Let me cook first.
- I want to hear it.

40:38.196 --> 40:41.375
- Right, cook first. I'm hungry.
- See?

40:42.875 --> 40:45.136
You sit as well. Why are you standing?

40:48.475 --> 40:52.208
- Tell me the story.
- You two carry on.

40:52.208 --> 40:54.575
- I'll close the door for you.
- Thank you.

40:56.475 --> 40:57.535
Tell me.

40:58.676 --> 41:03.331
I wanted to make this for you only.
Now it looks like you'll have to share.

41:03.355 --> 41:06.216
I like eating with everyone else.
Just tell me the story.

41:06.995 --> 41:10.331
- Let me cook first.
- Can't you talk while cooking?

41:10.355 --> 41:13.455
Of course not.
I need to focus while cooking.

41:14.515 --> 41:15.935
Do you like it a bit sweeter?

41:32.875 --> 41:34.816
This is for you. It's a bit sweeter.

41:44.596 --> 41:46.535
How long does it take to steam these?

41:47.636 --> 41:51.296
Over an hour. And they need to simmer
for another half an hour after that.

41:53.196 --> 41:56.296
Perfect. You can tell me the story now.
Go ahead, tell me.

42:00.035 --> 42:01.455
You know everything

42:03.636 --> 42:05.136
about what happened later.

42:08.276 --> 42:10.096
So we've known each other
for a long time.

42:13.216 --> 42:14.776
It's just that you were unaware.

42:30.475 --> 42:32.656
Did you compose this song?

42:35.276 --> 42:36.616
Did you mention it to him?

42:37.116 --> 42:39.455
Yes, she saved a few on my computer.
I listen to them often.

42:39.756 --> 42:43.051
Because working at the hospital
is usually tiring and busy.

42:43.075 --> 42:47.132
Listening to her songs relaxes me a lot.
It's a very nice pastime.

42:47.156 --> 42:49.816
We got to know each other
due to the songs she wrote.

42:50.796 --> 42:53.652
I'm one of her unknown fans.

42:53.676 --> 42:56.816
You told many lies just now.

42:56.995 --> 42:59.776
You're not one of my fans.

43:00.475 --> 43:02.256
They could be too easily found out.

43:03.075 --> 43:05.455
Some are true and some are false.

43:08.236 --> 43:10.495
If you hadn't told me, I wouldn't...

43:18.836 --> 43:20.935
Even if you have said it now,

43:23.676 --> 43:25.136
I dare not fully believe it.

43:36.236 --> 43:37.495
I will not lie to you.

43:39.555 --> 43:43.336
Qiang Qingci won't lie
to Shengshengman either.

44:12.550 --> 44:16.303
♪ Where should I start
about millions of dawns and dusks ♪

44:16.303 --> 44:18.160
♪ Depict a stroke
of rain before the mountain ♪

44:18.160 --> 44:20.292
♪ Stars beyond the sky ♪

44:20.624 --> 44:24.592
♪ Bit by bit, it outlines
yesterday and today ♪

44:24.592 --> 44:27.024
♪ And you with
picturesque eyebrows and eyes ♪

44:27.024 --> 44:30.083
♪ Jointly create the mood ♪

44:30.198 --> 44:33.919
♪ The rain and fog
over the mountains are intriguing ♪

44:33.919 --> 44:35.327
♪ It seems I can't get enough of seeing ♪

44:35.327 --> 44:37.918
♪ The once inexhaustible journey ♪

44:37.942 --> 44:38.981
♪ On this journey ♪

44:38.981 --> 44:40.677
♪ The stars accompany me
along thousands of miles ♪

44:40.677 --> 44:42.852
♪ I walk down with you ♪

44:42.852 --> 44:47.262
♪ Spending dawns and dusks together
for a hundred years ♪

44:47.286 --> 44:49.183
♪ Just like ♪

44:49.183 --> 44:50.113
♪ When the clouds are low ♪

44:50.113 --> 44:51.472
♪ It rains ♪

44:51.472 --> 44:55.728
♪ I was moved
when you were singing softly ♪

44:55.728 --> 44:59.440
♪ Since then, I hear stars every night ♪

44:59.440 --> 45:00.240
♪ And rains at midnight ♪

45:00.240 --> 45:05.996
♪ I could hear you
among millions of voices ♪

45:06.710 --> 45:09.185
♪ All other voices fade away ♪

45:09.185 --> 45:11.591
♪ I hear your monologue ♪

45:11.591 --> 45:15.536
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

45:15.536 --> 45:17.982
♪ Like knowing the implied meaning
of a picture ♪

45:17.982 --> 45:20.614
♪ Knowing your happiness and sadness ♪

45:20.614 --> 45:24.240
♪ Love comes in time again and again ♪

45:24.240 --> 45:26.896
♪ Among the millions of people ♪

45:26.896 --> 45:29.200
♪ I hear your voice ♪

45:29.200 --> 45:33.093
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

45:33.093 --> 45:35.344
♪ Tangled love for millions
of dawns and dusks ♪

45:35.344 --> 45:37.744
♪ Kisses like pouring rain ♪

45:37.744 --> 45:41.870
♪ Lightly falling
outside and inside the dream ♪

45:41.894 --> 45:44.369
♪ All other voices fade away ♪

45:44.369 --> 45:46.775
♪ I hear your monologue ♪

45:46.775 --> 45:50.672
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

45:50.672 --> 45:52.848
♪ Like knowing the implied meaning
