46:04.208 --> 46:08.144
♪ Saying I miss you so much ♪

46:08.144 --> 46:10.480
♪ Tangled love for millions
of dawns and dusks ♪

46:10.480 --> 46:12.944
♪ Kisses like pouring rain ♪

46:12.944 --> 46:16.272
♪ Lightly falling
outside and inside the dream ♪

46:16.272 --> 46:21.390
♪ With you in this life ♪

46:21.414 --> 46:24.139
♪ Tangled love for millions
